'''奧廖阿爾塞廖國際機場'''<ref name="twairinfo">{{cite web | title=Orio al Serio International Airport | url=http://twairinfo.com/airport01.php?id=275 | website=台灣民航資訊網 | language=zh-tw | access-date=2020-07-26 | archive-date=2020-07-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726120102/http://twairinfo.com/airport01.php?id=275 | dead-url=no }}</ref>（{{lang-it|Aeroporto di Bergamo Orio al Serio}}<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.aeroporto.net/aeroporto-bergamo-orio-al-serio/ | title=Aeroporto di Bergamo Orio al Serio | website=aeroporto.net | language=it | access-date=2020-07-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190510102909/https://www.aeroporto.net/aeroporto-bergamo-orio-al-serio/ | archive-date=2019-05-10 | dead-url=no }}</ref>；{{Airport codes|BGY|LIME}}），又稱'''卡拉瓦喬二世國際機場'''或'''米蘭貝加莫機場'''<ref name="airport-bergamo" />，位於[[奧廖阿爾塞廖|奧廖阿爾塞廖]]，是[[意大利|意大利]]第三大[[國際機場|國際機場]]，也是{{link-en|米蘭大都會區|Milan Metropolitan area}}內第二大機場<ref name="Stats">{{cite web | url=https://assaeroporti.com/wp-content/plugins/multipage_xls_reader/pdf_file/2019.pdf | title=Gennaio - Dicembre 2019 | website=www.assaeroporti.com | language=it | access-date=2020-07-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200426160213/https://assaeroporti.com/wp-content/plugins/multipage_xls_reader/pdf_file/2019.pdf | archive-date=2020-04-26 | dead-url=yes }}</ref> 。距離[[貝加莫|貝加莫]]市中心東南約4公里，[[米蘭|米蘭]]市中心東北約45公里<ref name="airport-bergamo">{{cite web | title=MILAN BERGAMO AIRPORT (BGY) | url=https://www.airport-bergamo.com/ | language=en | access-date=2020-07-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181017224832/https://www.airport-bergamo.com/ | archive-date=2018-10-17 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2019年，機場全年的客運量逾1380萬<ref name="Stats" />。

機場以[[低成本航空公司|低成本航空公司]]營運為主<ref name="regione-lombardia" />，2016年和2017年，機場更獲[[Skytrax|Skytrax]]選為全球十大最佳以低成本航空公司營運為主的客運樓之一。<ref name="bergamonews 20160411">{{cite news | script-title=it:L’aeroporto di Bergamo nella Top Ten di Skytrax | url=https://www.bergamonews.it/2016/04/11/laeroporto-di-bergamo-nella-top-ten-di-skytrax/220726/ | publisher=Bergamo News | language=it | date=2016-04-11 | access-date=2020-07-21 | archive-date=2020-07-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200721121809/https://www.bergamonews.it/2016/04/11/laeroporto-di-bergamo-nella-top-ten-di-skytrax/220726/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="skytrax2017">{{cite web | url=https://www.worldairportawards.com/Awards/best_lowcost_airports.html | title=The World's Best Airport Terminals for Low Cost airlines 2017 | access-date= | website=WorldAirportAwards | language=en | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170429154459/https://www.worldairportawards.com/Awards/best_lowcost_airports.html | archive-date=2017-04-29 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>[[瑞安航空|瑞安航空]]便以此機場作為意大利的樞紐機場。<ref name="airport-bergamo" />

== 歷史 ==
1937年，機場投入服務，但當時只作軍事用途<ref name="visitbergamo">{{Cite web | url=https://www.visitbergamo.net/en/object-details/8172-milan---bergamo-airport/ | title=MILAN - BERGAMO AIRPORT | website=visitbergamo.net | language=en | access-date=2020-07-21 | archive-date=2020-07-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726093848/https://www.visitbergamo.net/en/object-details/8172-milan---bergamo-airport/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>，而且實際只是個停機坪。到了1949年，有委員會提出改建使貝加莫擁有一個真正的機場，經過多年討論，在1970年7月16日，{{link-it|SACBO}}（{{lang|it|'''S'''ocietà per {{nowrap|l<nowiki>'</nowiki>'''a'''eroporto}} '''c'''ivile di '''B'''ergamo-'''O'''rio}}）成立<ref name="milantoday 20200717">{{cite web | url=https://www.milanotoday.it/attualita/orio-al-serio-50-anni.html | title=I primi 50 anni di Orio al Serio, diventato il terzo aeroporto italiano: festa con un nuovo ampliamento | publisher=MILANO TODAY | language=it | date=2020-07-17 | access-date=2020-07-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200719094415/http://www.milanotoday.it/attualita/orio-al-serio-50-anni.html | archive-date=2020-07-19 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，數月後在1971年，機場成為了民用機場<ref name="visitbergamo" />。1972年3月21日，首班民航飛機從貝加莫機場起飛飛往[[羅馬-錢皮諾機場|羅馬-錢皮諾機場]]，標誌着機場民航服務的開始。<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.bergamonews.it/2012/03/20/sacbo-quarantanni-fail-primo-volo-bergamo-roma/158343/ | script-title=it:Sacbo, quarant’anni fa il primo volo Bergamo-Roma | publisher=Bergamo News | language=it | date=2012-03-20 | access-date=2020-07-22 | archive-date=2020-07-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726095406/https://www.bergamonews.it/2012/03/20/sacbo-quarantanni-fail-primo-volo-bergamo-roma/158343/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>

1990年代，機場得到了8000萬投資，擴闊了跑道和增加了機場設施。1999年，機場首次超越了全年100萬的客運量<ref name="milantoday 20200717" />。2001年，機場更獲客運行業的質素認證。<ref name="simpleflying 20191126">{{cite web | title=How Milan Bergamo Airport Grew 1,300% In Two Decades | first=Joanna | last=Bailey | url=https://simpleflying.com/how-milan-bergamo-airport-grew-1300-in-two-decades/ | website=Simple Flying | date=2019-11-26 | access-date=2020-07-22 | language=en | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209141831/https://simpleflying.com/how-milan-bergamo-airport-grew-1300-in-two-decades/ | archive-date=2019-12-09 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

2002年2月14日，[[瑞安航空|瑞安航空]]營運首班由[[法蘭克福-哈恩機場|法蘭克福-哈恩機場]]飛往貝加莫機場的航班。在此以後，機場吸引到了更多低成本航空公司，例如[[維茲航空|維茲航空]]的進駐。<ref name="simpleflying 20191126" />機場亦隨之成為了意大利最重要的低成本航班機場。<ref name="bergamonews 20160411" />2009年，米蘭貝加莫機場的客運量達到了全意大利第四。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.assaeroporti.it/ViewPasseggeriProg.asp?mese=12&anno=2009&lingua=it | title=PASSEGGERI (Gennaio-Dicembre/2009) | language=it | website=assaeroporti.it | access-date= | archive-url=https://archive.is/20120905133507/http://www.assaeroporti.it/ViewPasseggeriProg.asp?mese=12&anno=2009&lingua=it | archive-date=2012-09-05 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>

2011年3月23日，{{link-en|意大利民航局|Italian Civil Aviation Authority}}（ENAC）宣佈將機場的正式名稱改至「貝加莫奧廖阿爾塞廖卡拉瓦喬二世國際機場」（{{lang|en|{{nowrap|Il Caravaggio}} International Airport Bergamo Orio al Serio}}），名稱取自著名畫家[[卡拉瓦喬|米開朗基羅·梅里西·達·卡拉瓦喬]]。<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.ecodibergamo.it/stories/Cronaca/193776_dal_23_marzo_laeroporto_di_orio/ | title=Dal 23 marzo l'aeroporto di Orio è intitolato al pittore Caravaggio | publisher=L'ECO DI BERGAMO | date=2011-03-23 | access-date=2020-07-22 | language=it | archive-date=2021-10-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211027115026/https://www.ecodibergamo.it/stories/Cronaca/193776_dal_23_marzo_laeroporto_di_orio/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>

2015年，機場的全年客運量超過了1000萬<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.lavocedibergamo.it/attualita/orio-al-serio-raggiunti-i-10-milioni-di-passeggeri-nell-anno.html | title=Orio al Serio: raggiunti i 10 milioni di passeggeri nell'anno | language=it | date=2015-12-18 | access-date= | publisher=La Voce di Bergamo | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160917201955/http://www.lavocedibergamo.it/attualita/orio-al-serio-raggiunti-i-10-milioni-di-passeggeri-nell-anno.html | archive-date=2016-09-17 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>，成為了意大利第三大機場<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.italy24.ilsole24ore.com/art/business-and-economy/2016-01-22/italian-airport-traffic-increased-2015-bergamo-rises-to-third-place-183745.php?uuid=ACw3BbFC | title=Italian airport traffic increased in 2015, Bergamo rises to third place | first=Marco | last=Morino | publisher=italy24.ilsole24ore.com | date=2016-01-23 | access-date=2020-07-22 | language=en }}</ref>。2016和2017年，更連續兩年獲英國顧問公司[[Skytrax|Skytrax]]選為全球十大最佳低成本航空公司客運樓。<ref name="bergamonews 20160411" /><ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.worldairportawards.com/Awards/best_lowcost_airports.html | title=The World's Best Airports Terminals for Low Cost airlines 2016 | website=WorldAirportAwards | access-date= | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160410012818/https://www.worldairportawards.com/Awards/best_lowcost_airports.html | archive-date=2016-04-10 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="skytrax2017" />

